{"tid":988954,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解古中國出產唔到西方個種全身鎧甲","createTime":"2019-01-20T13:26:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T09:38:47.000Z","uid":67500,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"ef6677cdfd0f8381f28f55b29a4739be90667de2","tid":988954,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T13:26:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.madefuns.com/uploads/allimg/160129/1-160129145309557.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.madefuns.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F160129%2F1-160129145309557.jpg&h=4cc52a9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/tfscom/i1/T1XJuaFANXXXXXXXXX_!!0-item_pic.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.alicdn.com%2Ftfscom%2Fi1%2FT1XJuaFANXXXXXXXXX_%21%210-item_pic.jpg&h=0710a4d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a9ddbcb7d5fb70b9c6425b50f6c0fd7a4d6e81c","tid":988954,"uid":9315,"like":79,"dislike":6,"score":73,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T13:29:57.000Z","msg":"西方騎兵係貴族黎  佢地怕死先有全身鎧甲<br />\n中國士兵係平民黎  條命賤過一副鎧甲  好似係<br />\nbtw 冇唔等於整唔到既"},{"pid":"984f1e6468e818dc38d5526e446f90664e9b3c93","tid":988954,"uid":124114,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T13:30:02.000Z","msg":"好似話全副盔甲其實得貴族同近衛先有,真係前線果D唔係咁"},{"pid":"67e4ded7865372d7c32dc15e40f615913f0306be","tid":988954,"uid":46500,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T13:31:53.000Z","msg":"中國西周先有貴族打仗 但果陣冇盔甲<br />\n<br />\n到有盔甲果陣已經係平民軍人"},{"pid":"4428157334c2a489680999c2e181e4a4cf6ae00b","tid":988954,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T13:41:42.000Z","msg":"御林軍有"},{"pid":"6e62367708bf1c090e06b76c93815f1b67e78a36","tid":988954,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T13:49:29.000Z","msg":"9估騎馬先用咁重甲啫<br />\n步兵咁重點頂<br />\n同埋鐵礦同士兵既比例問題？"},{"pid":"dbda689696ac239def4e2e58f7dbb49b59d01065","tid":988954,"uid":61232,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score