1db33fb974e043c12db573","tid":988954,"uid":212317,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"37bc6337fa881291a3d1f2d5af1b4c2e88f5d31c","tid":988954,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":55,"score":-55,"quote":{"pid":"e87322b714bc2b315c2a63f6a707dba62480c495","tid":988954,"uid":12599,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T02:35:31.000Z","msg":"歐洲重騎俾蒙古突騎打到hihi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一跌落地基本上就玩完，中國西漢果時已經知呢d重騎打遊牧民族唔work<br />\n<br />\n清國套八旗甲其實係馬上面夠cover全身，仲要輕咁多"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T02:43:28.000Z","msg":"歐洲同蒙古有打過咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T02:45:05.000Z","msg":"有 鬼佬完敗"},{"pid":"6405099d9047226f113c88c67db3bbf00c0c7008","tid":988954,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T02:47:45.000Z","msg":"打烏龜"},{"pid":"699716ef3b0ac86774548c7b92f26be2ffd8e89a","tid":988954,"uid":138790,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:45:09.000Z","msg":"首先蒙古時期未有全身板甲<br />\n其次中世紀後期因為火器啲甲重到要吊條友上馬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n事實上上面嘅謬論係來自勞倫斯&middot;奧利維爾係1944年嘅電影亨利五世<br />\n(<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SGnLKGOlldU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSGnLKGOlldU&d=pNYsN7luP6RpznWW5VEjr%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=338d498f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SGnLKGOlldU</a> 1:24:55開始)<br />\n,但係事實上係大錯特錯,與史不乎,因為係莎翁原著入面係講明騎士係自行上馬,事實上係導演自己亂改,根本唔係歷史<br />\n事實上因為全身板甲年代近(直至十七世紀仲有人用),又多實物(主流嘅米蘭式有好多,但係哥特式就比較少),歐洲好多人做歷史復刻去玩HMA或者做歷史研究<br />\n例如<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5hlIUrd7d1Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5hlIUrd7d1Q&d=pNYsN7luP6RpznWW5VEjr%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=906511e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5hlIUrd7d1Q</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qzTwBQniLSc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqzTwBQniLSc&d=pNYsN7luP6RpznWW5VEjr%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=a52fdb9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qzTwBQniLSc</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q-bnM5SuQkI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dq-bnM5SuQkI&d=pNYsN7luP6RpznWW5VEjr%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=9c4cc38c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q-bnM5SuQkI</a><br />\n前空翻上梯攀石都做到,結果上唔到馬?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係個句 歐洲人又唔傻仔,唔會用一樣打唔到仗嘅武器上戰場去等死<br />\n而<br />\nA complete suit of plate armour made from well-tempered steel would weigh around 15&ndash;25 kg(33-55lbs)(James, Lawrence (2003). Warrior Race: A History of the British at War. St. Martin's Press. p. 119. ISBN 0-312-30737-3.),唔好話30kg,係連30kg都無,對於一個職業士兵黎講算係一個好正常嘅負重<br />\n比如,十五世紀末嘅全身式騎士板甲-馬克西米利安式板甲(Maximilian Armour)已經將重量控制到20公斤左右(圖說西洋甲胄武器事典,近代-馬克西米利安式板甲)<br />\n再者,米蘭式板甲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hk3tCyG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhk3tCyG.jpg&h=24998766&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n哥特式板甲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pbqorr1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPbqorr1.jpg&h=05575220&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n關節充滿弱點?GAY?唔係關節都以板甲防護做咩?<br />\n明明歐洲咁多板甲實物就睇下先講<br />\n而且上面講都只係全身板甲,仲未計當時更流行嘅四分三板甲(即係捨棄下半身防具嘅騎兵甲),大部份重量都係20公斤以下,負量同現代步兵差唔多<br />\n而30公斤盔甲重唔重?<br />\n以宋代士兵做例(無文物只好局住史書考證)<br />\n別皮線穿舉全成里<span style=\"color: red;\">五十八斤內兩至五叩一斤八</span>(宋會要 五十三)<br />\n宋代步兵甲重達三十公斤(宋一斤為633g,一兩為40g),比歐洲騎士嘅板甲仲要重好多,仲要係步兵甲,又唔見佢地打唔到仗?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係造謠一張嘴,闢謠跑斷腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a74fa632adc8854970a58ad2dffbe58114d320","tid":988954,"uid":208722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"37bc6337fa881291a3d1f2d5af1b4c2e88f5d31c","tid":988954,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":55,"score":-55,"quote":{"pid":"e87322b714bc2b315c2a63f6a707dba62480c495","tid":988954,"uid":12599,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T02:35:31.000Z","msg":"歐洲重騎俾蒙古突騎打到hihi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一跌落地基本上就玩完，中國西漢果時已經知呢d重騎打遊牧民族唔work<br />\n<br />\n清國套八旗甲其實係馬上面夠cover全身，仲要輕咁多"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T02:43:28.000Z","msg":"歐洲同蒙古有打過咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:52:37.000Z","msg":"Do research before 9upping"},{"pid":"99e8f16c7c32a2ca97c0b85e529a58c78b71b792","tid":988954,"uid":138790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T08:33:39.000Z","msg":"上面仲要有人話西漢重騎打唔過遊牧輕騎兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首先戰場唔係遊戲,咩時候都係講究多兵種協同<br />\n另外西漢時候漢軍有重裝騎兵,有突擊騎兵?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本無西漢又點知重騎打唔過輕騎<br />\n夫平原易地，輕車突騎，則匈奴之眾易撓亂也;勁弩長戟，射疏及遠，則匈奴之弓弗能格也;堅甲利刃，長短相雜，遊弩往來，什伍俱前，則匈奴之兵弗能當也;材官騶發，矢道同的，則匈奴之革笥木薦弗能支也;下馬地鬬，劍戟相接，去就相薄，則匈奴之足弗能給也：。此中國之長技也以此觀之，匈奴之長技三，中國之長技五陛下又興數十萬之眾，以誅數万之匈奴，眾寡之計，以一擊十之術也。晃錯-言兵事疏<br />\n事實上係平原正面對抗,漢軍體系係有優勢<br />\n七年冬，上自往擊，破信軍銅鞮，斬其將王喜。信亡走匈奴。（與）其與白土人曼丘臣、王黃等立趙苗裔趙利為王，復收信敗散兵，而與信及冒頓謀攻漢。匈奴仗左右賢王將萬餘騎與王黃等屯廣武以南，<span style=\"color: red;\">至晉陽，與漢兵戰，漢大破之，追至于離石，復破之。匈奴復聚兵樓煩西北，漢令車騎擊破匈奴。匈奴常敗走，漢乘勝追北</span>(史記韓信盧綰列傳)<br />\n而且重騎兵打唔嬴輕騎兵,咁亞歷山大嘅國王騎兵.羅馬同安息同具裝騎兵用念力打嬴遊牧民族?"},{"pid":"445618fc4b5aa4e4e823603a657b84f49c50ee91","tid":988954,"uid":5649,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T08:35:38.000Z","msg":"好心吹奏鬼佬搵第二樣啦<br />\n古中國喺有熱兵器之前唔差得過西方"},{"pid":"6aa1714526a0ff91598caa4e40e8ea343884899e","tid":988954,"uid":7934,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T08:42:25.000Z","msg":"去愛沙尼亞古城有間博物館有得試著鎧甲，只係個頭盔都已經重到拎唔到頭"},{"pid":"708ca0f3fc2ef7a292d19196f150f942f57d0952","tid":988954,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T08:44:46.000Z","msg":"西方有甲著都係貴族或獲封騎士<br />\n其他只係平民 俘虜 傭兵"},{"pid":"b842ebed4aff4aafcd824d77ed8172cf5f92adeb","tid":988954,"uid":34666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e87322b714bc2b315c2a63f6a707dba62480c495","tid":988954,"uid":12599,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T02:35:31.000Z","msg":"歐洲重騎俾蒙古突騎打到hihi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一跌落地基本上就玩完，中國西漢果時已經知呢d重騎打遊牧民族唔work<br />\n<br />\n清國套八旗甲其實係馬上面夠cover全身，仲要輕咁多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T08:58:03.000Z","msg":"成吉思汗年代蒙古重騎兵係仲重甲過同期歐洲重騎兵"},{"pid":"8879f225cf7530cbe80e232aa72070a11e37b8be","tid":988954,"uid":34666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6aa1714526a0ff91598caa4e40e8ea343884899e","tid":988954,"uid":7934,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T08:42:25.000Z","msg":"去愛沙尼亞古城有間博物館有得試著鎧甲，只係個頭盔都已經重到拎唔到頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T08:59:10.000Z","msg":"板甲輕過魚鱗甲"},{"pid":"f0b52b60caa308f8c82838fee15cccf65921b7b3","tid":988954,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a9ddbcb7d5fb70b9c6425b50f6c0fd7a4d6e81c","tid":988954,"uid":9315,"like":79,"dislike":6,"score":73,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T13:29:57.000Z","msg":"西方騎兵係貴族黎  佢地怕死先有全身鎧甲<br />\n中國士兵係平民黎  條命賤過一副鎧甲  好似係<br />\nbtw 冇唔等於整唔到既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:07:04.000Z","ms